I also get the error in projects that were created from scratch without spaces in any names. Shall I share with you a Google Drive folder with my project in it?

Hi all,

I just wanted to say that I'm in the same boat as @xneven in that I've still not resolved this issue at my end, even with fresh installs of DLC and non-spaced labelling. In fact I seem to have gone backwards as now the labelling GUI freezes after labelling a few frames. I'm hoping that that has something to do with the remote access situation that I have right now, so I'm due to go in and work on things 'in situ' soon.
